	<p>Prerequisites: <CourseLink id={1711} href="/BENG#126A">BENG 126A</CourseLink>; concurrent enrollment in <CourseLink id={1754} href="/BENG#187C">BENG 187C</CourseLink>; bioengineering or bioengineering: biotechnology majors only or consent of instructor. (W)</p>
